Global Foam Fire Extinguishing Equipment Market Insights
Foam Fire Extinguishing Equipment Market size was valued at USD 1.20 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 1.95 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 7.5% from 2024 to 2030.

Foam Fire Extinguishing Equipment Market Overview
The global Foam Fire Extinguishing Equipment Market size was valued at USD 2.8 billion in 2023 and is projected to grow at a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 4.6% from 2024 to 2030. This growth is driven by increasing industrial activities, stringent fire safety regulations, and advancements in foam technology. The market includes various foam-based fire suppression systems, such as Aqueous Film-Forming Foam (AFFF), Protein Foam, and others, catering to industries like oil & gas, manufacturing, aviation, and chemical plants.

